            "title": "Resort Wear Designed for Life by the Water",
            "title_heading": true,
            "accordion_enabled": true,
            "text": "<p>Our beach and resort wear collection brings together everything you need for days spent under the sun — and nights that linger by the sea. Designed to flow with your lifestyle, these pieces combine comfort, performance, and style to take you effortlessly from the ocean to everyday life.</p><p>Pair your favourite one piece swimsuit or triangle bikini top with lightweight women’s jogger pants, a resort sarong, or wide-legged lounge pants for a look that feels as luxurious as it looks. Every piece is made to complement your swimwear — versatile, breathable, and consciously crafted for movement and ease.</p>",
