            "text": "<p>'I came back after buying two Sulawesi long sleeve swimsuits and bought a white pair of these.</p><p>They are triple-lined so no see through and are so soft and comfortable given the fabric and elasticised waist.</p><p>The price is amazing too! I will wear them to work with a nice flat, or by the pool. So versatile!!</p><p>I highly recommend!!'</p>",
