            "title": "BeauTifully designed",
            "text": "<p>Supportive, feel-good, and a beautiful piece. I’ve been wearing this both as a top with shorts, and as a bikini at beach & at a spa! Makes me feel beautiful wearing! Love both the top and bottom! 💗</p>",
