    "image_with_text_mA3LjV": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "name": "Image with text",
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/Triangle_string_bikini_green.png",
        "image_position": "left",
        "image_size": "medium",
        "image_height": "fixed",
        "desktop_image_height": 450,
        "mobile_image_height": 450,
        "title": "Why Women Love Ocean Soul Resort Wear",
        "text": "<h4>Flattering, Functional & Designed to Move</h4><p>Our resort wear is built for women who value both comfort and confidence. Whether you’re styling a surf bikini top under a resort sarong or pairing a boyfriend tee with wide-legged lounge pants, these pieces are created for easy, effortless elegance.</p><p>Flattering Silhouettes: Relaxed cuts that complement your swimwear and flatter all body types.<br/></p><p>Breathable Fabrics: Lightweight materials that keep you cool and comfortable in the tropics.<br/></p><p>Day-to-Night Versatility: Mix and match separates that move seamlessly from morning beach walks to sunset drinks.</p>",
        "button_text": "Button",
        "link": "",
        "center_align": true,
        "text_color": "#606060",
        "background_color": "#f7f7f7"
      }
    },
    "image_with_text_ggG8gy": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "name": "Image with text",
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/sumatra_cropped_943929b4-04e9-4bbf-aaeb-74f14effa103.jpg",
        "image_position": "right",
        "image_size": "medium",
        "image_height": "fixed",
        "desktop_image_height": 450,
        "mobile_image_height": 450,
        "title": "Sustainable Materials, Conscious Craftsmanship",
        "text": "<p>We believe luxury should never come at the planet’s expense. Every piece of Ocean Soul resort wear is made using eco-friendly fabrics - from breathable natural fibres to regenerated materials that stand up to the elements.</p><p>Each garment is:</p><p>Ethically Handmade in Bali by skilled local artisans.<br/></p><p>Produced in Small Batches to reduce waste and ensure exceptional quality.<br/></p><p>Durable & Fade-Resistant, holding shape and colour season after season.<br/></p><p>Our swimwear is crafted from luxurious Italian recycled fabric, offering UPF 50+ sun protection and superior resistance to salt, chlorine, and sun exposure. Whether you’re wearing a one piece swimwear style or a high-waisted bikini bottom, you can feel confident knowing every piece aligns with your values.</p>",
        "button_text": "Button",
        "link": "",
        "center_align": true,
        "text_color": "#606060",
        "background_color": "#f7f7f7"
      }
    },
    "image_with_text_w9RxgX": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "name": "Image with text",
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/black_sarong_meno_ocean_soul_bali.jpg",
        "image_position": "left",
        "image_size": "medium",
        "image_height": "fixed",
        "desktop_image_height": 450,
        "mobile_image_height": 450,
        "title": "Designed to Pair with Your Swimwear",
        "text": "<p>Our beach and resort wear is made to complement your swim collection. Every piece layers beautifully with your triangle bikini top, low rise bikini, or one piece swimsuit, helping you build outfits that transition effortlessly from the ocean to out-and-about.</p><p>Poolside: Layer your surf bikini top with a flowing resort sarong and slides.<br/></p><p>Relaxed Lunch: Pair a boyfriend tee with women’s jogger pants for effortless beach café style.<br/></p><p>Evening Escape: Elevate your look with wide-legged lounge pants, strappy sandals, and a bamboo clutch - proof that resort wear can be as chic as it is comfortable.<br/></p><p>Every combination is designed for versatility, allowing you to create dozens of looks from a few thoughtfully chosen pieces.</p>",
        "button_text": "Button",
        "link": "",
        "center_align": true,
        "text_color": "#606060",
        "background_color": "#f7f7f7"
      }
    },
    "image_with_text_4CKW7J": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "name": "Image with text",
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/Misool_White.jpg",
        "image_position": "right",
        "image_size": "medium",
        "image_height": "fixed",
        "desktop_image_height": 450,
        "mobile_image_height": 450,
        "title": "Made for Real Women, Made to Last",
        "text": "<p>Our community of ocean-loving women inspires every design. From surfers and swimmers to travellers and sun-seekers, Ocean Soul pieces are made to fit into your life - and stay with you through every season.</p><p>Expect:</p><p>Sculpting Fits that move with you, never against you.<br/></p><p>Soft, Seamless Construction for comfort that lasts all day.<br/></p><p>Timeless Styles that never go out of fashion.<br/></p><p>Each piece is tested for performance and durability, ensuring that your resort sarong, tote wet bag, or boyfriend tee remains a wardrobe staple, year after year.</p>",
        "button_text": "Button",
        "link": "",
        "center_align": true,
        "text_color": "#606060",
        "background_color": "#f7f7f7"
      }
    },
    "image_with_text_overlay_Adzym7": {
      "type": "image-with-text-overlay",
      "name": "Image with text overlay",
      "settings": {
        "full_width": true,
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/The_meno_black_and_white.jpg",
        "overlay": true,
        "background_attachment": "fixed",
        "height": 400,
        "mobile_height": 400,
        "text_align": "center",
        "caption_vertical": 50,
        "caption_horizontal": 50,
        "heading": "The Ocean Soul Way",
        "subheading_text": "<p>We don’t believe in throwaway fashion - we believe in pieces that travel with you, season after season. Every design in our beach resort wear collection is made to pair effortlessly with your sustainable swimwear, creating a capsule wardrobe that works anywhere, anytime.</p><p>From the sculpting lines of a one piece swimsuit to the relaxed drape of a women’s jogger pant, every garment embodies what Ocean Soul stands for: performance, purpose, and effortless style.</p><p>Because true resort wear isn’t just about how you look - it’s about how you feel.</p>",
        "button_text": "Button",
