            "text": "<h3></h3><p>Discover resort-ready pieces that redefine sustainable luxury:</p><p>One Piece Swimwear & Surf Bikini Tops for active days in the water.<br/></p><p>High-Waisted Bikini Bottoms and Low-Rise Bikinis for mix-and-match versatility.<br/></p><p>Women’s Jogger Pants, Wide-Leg Lounge Pants, and Resort Sarongs for comfort and ease.<br/></p><p>Boyfriend Tees, Tote Wet Bags, and Bamboo Clutches for those finishing touches that make an outfit complete.<br/></p><p>Every piece is made to move with you - from ocean to everyday, effortlessly.</p>",
